{"tid":1504680,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"咪撚再恥笑水炮車廢","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T19:53:50.000Z","uid":116910,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec421340dbf4afd53727f36a8d7f9dc82e3b897","tid":1504680,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"今日係第一次用<br />\n所有人mon撚住<br />\n再加上控制隻狗分分鐘都未射過真人<br />\n<br />\n所以先細細力比人覺得威力唔大<br />\n係幫手足濕身only<br />\n<br />\n正如第一次出催淚彈（近年）<br />\n佔中個次 各界嘩然<br />\n宜家？ 催淚彈當講早晨<br />\n<br />\n去到過兩個星期各界開始慣左成日出動水炮<br />\n到時就黎料<br />\n骨折爆頭爆眼就唔再有人理<br />\n<br />\n邊個再恥笑水炮車廢我就屌邊個老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要保持警覺 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d990d1d76e656ba72a3034f503adac43e04bb677","tid":1504680,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"p1sh"},{"pid":"16a48195f180687cd4b53ad31eb5797d2082610a","tid":1504680,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"p2sh"},{"pid":"f81411cc98f604b32fda27df78642c9be700b7d6","tid":1504680,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"p3sh"},{"pid":"98687173fb56f90f3a910a01733ef278a03bafde","tid":1504680,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489dfec75945a2e2b5acbd941d0111f21a454f10","tid":1504680,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"P4sh"},{"pid":"a11f9343f253a73b7ea5d42ecd669ed6cb368d08","tid":1504680,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"欲擒故縱"},{"pid":"abe5184b12592423148463f2